    "Table 3 presents the frequency of identified occupations based on unique tweets.",
    "We delved into the most popular topics within different occupations, showing how they might differ from the most popular topics in the overall tweets observed in Table 1.",
    "To achieve this, we analyzed the topics identified by the BERTopic in Section 4.2, focusing specifically on those found within tweets from users with each defined occupation.",
    "We excluded the ubiquitous AI and ChatGPT topic to maintain consistency with our previous findings.",
    "The key findings are summarized in Table 4."
